      <h2>混合式技術架構：四層分工骨架</h2>
      <p style="color:var(--t2);font-size:1rem;margin-top:.55rem;max-width:72ch">以下架構是由 <a href="https://www.rgare.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">RGA</a>、<a href="https://www.munichre.com/en/solutions/for-insurance-industry/allfinanz.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Munich Re</a>、<a href="https://www.metlife.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">MetLife</a>、<a href="https://cloud.google.com/agent-assist" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google</a>、<a href="https://aws.amazon.com/connect/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">AWS</a> 等公開案例共同指向的實務骨架，<strong>非單一廠商宣稱</strong>。每層的邊界是台灣壽險 AI 治理的核心議題。<span class="tag t-inf">inferred</span></p>
    </div>
    <div class="arch-svg-wrap rv">
      <svg id="arch-svg" width="100%" viewBox="0 0 1060 340" style="min-width:860px;display:block"></svg>
