    <div class="ga rv2" style="margin-top:1.2rem">
      <div class="card" style="border-top:2px solid #2d6a4f">
        <h4>規則引擎 Rules Engine</h4>
        <p style="font-size:.88rem;color:var(--t2)">最終可審計決策閘門。固化明確規則。<em>主要失敗模式：規則老化、例外累積過多</em></p>
        <p style="font-size:.82rem;color:var(--t3);margin-bottom:0">案例：<a href="https://www.rgare.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">RGA Aura Next</a> · <a href="https://www.munichre.com/en/solutions/for-insurance-industry/allfinanz.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Munich Re ALLFINANZ</a> · <a href="https://www.swissre.com/life-health/underwriting/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Swiss Re Magnum</a></p>
      </div>
      <div class="card" style="border-top:2px solid #1e4d91">
        <h4>機器學習 ML Scoring</h4>
        <p style="font-size:.88rem;color:var(--t2)">風險排序、詐欺評分、STP 候選篩選。輸出建議與排序，<strong>不做最終決策</strong>。<em>主要失敗模式：模型漂移、訓練偏差</em></p>
        <p style="font-size:.82rem;color:var(--t3);margin-bottom:0">案例：<a href="https://www.massmutual.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">MassMutual</a> 演算法核保 · <a href="https://www.munichre.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Munich Re Predictor</a> · <a href="https://www.shift-technology.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Shift</a> 詐欺評分</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card" style="border-top:2px solid #6b3fa0">
