        <p style="font-size:.88rem;color:var(--t2)">摘要、知識檢索、文件理解、客服建議草稿。定位為<strong>輔助性</strong>，不做保險決策。<em>主要失敗模式：幻覺、知識庫過舊</em></p>
        <p style="font-size:.82rem;color:var(--t3);margin-bottom:0">案例：<a href="https://cloud.google.com/agent-assist" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Agent Assist</a> · <a href="https://aws.amazon.com/bedrock/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Amazon Bedrock</a> · <a href="https://www.genesys.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Genesys Copilot</a></p>
