        <p style="font-size:.82rem;color:var(--t3);margin-bottom:0">法規依據：保險業 AI 自律規範 · <a href="https://www.rgare.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">RGA</a> 官方明寫 monitoring/logging <span class="tag ta">A</span><span class="tag tb">B</span></p>
